      "description": "CFD-predicted hemolysis index compared against in vitro measurement at operating point 2. Predicted MIH = 0.0044 g/100L versus experimental 0.0041 g/100L; relative error 7.3%. Aleatory variability in RBC fragility across donor samples acknowledged in prose discussion only."
