      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison metric (e.g., E_rel or validation metric u_val) computed with experimental uncertainty bounds; metric must demonstrate agreement within combined uncertainty at all five operating points.",
      "rationale": "Relative errors range 4.8%–10.7% across five operating points. Experimental uncertainty bars reported for three of five points; two points lack replicate measurements needed to estimate aleatory spread. Formal validation metric not computed against combined uncertainty band. Achieved level 3."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
