      "rationale": "FDA generic pump geometry used in both simulation and experiment — geometry match confirmed. Operating conditions span the VAD envelope. However, porcine blood used in experiments rather than human blood; species-specific RBC fragility differences introduce unquantified aleatory uncertainty. Achieved level 2 against required level 5."
